- cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is the most likely category as the paper deals with intersection graphs of convex sets in the plane and their recognition.
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is also likely as the paper involves studying the Clique problem in intersection graphs.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper discusses the complexity of the Clique problem in different types of intersection graphs.
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is a possibility as the paper involves finding the maximum clique in intersection graphs, which is a problem in game theory.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a possibility as the paper discusses the NP-completeness of the Clique problem in certain types of intersection graphs.
